    "description": "building your first app doesn’t have to cost thousands\n \nhere’s the exact stack i’d use today:\n\n→ claude for coding ($20/mo) \n→ supabase for the database (free tier) \n→ superwall for the paywall (free until you’re making money) \n→ apple developer subscription ($99/yr)\n\nthat’s it. under $150 total to go from idea to app store.\n\nmost people overthink this. they wait until they have the “perfect” setup. \n\nmeanwhile someone with less skill and this exact stack is shipping.\n\ncomment “list” and i’ll DM you the full list\n#claude #mobileapp #aitools",
